1- $ laravel new backend
2- $ ng new frontend
3- setting JWT (JSON Web Token Authentication for Laravel & Lumen).
    (https://github.com/tymondesigns/jwt-auth)
    
    //there is two wayas 
    1- got ducs copy and past at terminal
        $ composer require tymon/jwt-auth
4- installing bootstrap on frontend using npm
    a) $ npm install bootstrap
    b) goto src/style.css and import bootstrap
        @import '~/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css'

5- running the ng-server
    $ ng serve -o

    